  <brief_title>Fistulectomy vs. Modified Karydakis Procedure for Pilonidal Sinus</brief_title>
  <official_title>Two Surgical Techniques for the Treatment of Pilinidal Sinus: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
